Scenario: Successful Login
  Given the user is on the login page 
  the user enters the username as "administareur" And the user enters the password as "motpass" And the user clicks the "Se connecter" button 
  Then the user should be logged in successfully

Scenario: Invalid Login Credentials 
  Given the user is on the login page 
  When the user enters the username as "administareur" And the user enters the password as "aaaa" And the user clicks the "Se connecter" button 
  Then the page should display "Invalid credentials"

Scenario: Invalid Login Credentials with username "bbbbb" 
 Given the user is on the login page 
 When the user enters the username as "bbbbb" And the user enters the password as "aaaa" And the user clicks the "Se connecter" button 
 the page should display "Invalid credentials"
 
Scenario: Successful Logout 
 Given the user is on the profile page 
 When the user clicks on the profile button And the user clicks on the logout button 
 Then the user should be logged out of the system